Release notes for gdcd 0.2.1
----------------------------

New releases and additional information available at:
http://gdcd.undergrid.net/

gdcd 0.2.1 can display cover art using either GdkPixbuf or Imlib.  It will use
GdkPixbuf by default if both are available due to memory leak problems with
Imlib.  You must have one of these installed.

For additional information on installation and required dependancies, please
read the INSTALL file.

All comments/praise/complaints/bug reports/suggestions/etc. should be sent to:
bascule@inferno.tusculum.edu
